{"tid":2034891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★網民投訴大量 IOS App 無法開啟！竟要求重新購買","createTime":"2020-05-25T13:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T10:45:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1366ce93c7fdb09d3959454887326112179dc265","tid":2034891,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pc3mag.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/iphone-app-this-app-is-no-longer-shared-bug_00a-768x403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fiphone-app-this-app-is-no-longer-shared-bug_00a-768x403.jpg&h=b8c16f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近有很多 iOS 裝置用戶投訴完全不能開 App，他們在開 App 之前看到一個警告標語「This app is no longer shared with you.」，著用戶在 App Store 重新購買。有網民在 MacRumors 討論區和 Twitter 分享他們無法開 App 的問題，更指就算跟隨指示入 App Store，也只看到「開啟」按鈕。<br />\n<br />\n受影響的裝置包括 iOS 13.4.1 和 iOS 13.5，未知是否有更多用戶受影響，受影響的 App 包括 YouTube、Twitter、WhatsApp、Facebook、TikTok、LastPass 等等，未知這是與證書到期或其他問題有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://pc3mag.com/iphone-app-this-app-is-no-longer-shared-bug/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fiphone-app-this-app-is-no-longer-shared-bug%2F&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3iNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=2b6481cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pc3mag.com/iphone-app-this-app-is-no-longer-shared-bug/</a>"},{"pid":"f3745ac3ed183050c25234137b3ee4f94456e0ad","tid":2034891,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nneed回血？"},{"pi